```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant MQ as Broker
  participant C as Consumer
  participant R as Redis
  participant X as Side Effect

  MQ-->>C: Deliver message (message_id)
  C->>R: SETNX processed:{message_id} = 1 (TTL)
  alt already processed
    R-->>C: 0 (exists)
    C-->>MQ: ACK (skip)
  else first time
    R-->>C: 1 (created)
    C->>X: Apply side effect (idempotent if possible)
    alt success
      C-->>MQ: ACK
    else failure
      C->>R: DEL processed:{message_id} (optional)
      C-->>MQ: NACK / retry
    end
  end
```
